data.description: CUL-DE-SAC living! This 3 bed 2 bath Elko home boasts over 1700 sq ft, 2 car garage, and .2 acre city lot. New vinyl flooring and custom kitchen cabinetry. Spacious formal living room boasts vaulted ceilings and large bay window allowing tons of natural light in. Newly remodeled kitchen offers matching black appliances. Dining area just off of kitchen. Master is large and master bath offers newly tiled shower/tub combo and single sink vanity. Downstairs you'll find the spacious family room with fireplace and a richer darker patterned vinyl flooring. The level below that offers 3rd large bedroom and laundry room. Home has a HUGE back deck, an ideal space for entertaining or just sipping your morning coffee. Fully fenced back yard with sprinkler system. Pad and 220V hook up in backyard for future hot tub. Washer and dryer to stay. Refrigerator in home does not stay. Seller will replace it with fridge from home they are purchasing with acceptable offer if buyer wants. THIS HOME IS GORGEOUS nestled in a cup-de-sac neighborhood and WONT LAST LONG. Sale is contingent upon sellers finding and successfully getting new home under contract.
